x4freetext: Scattering chamber filled with H2 or He which pressure
is adjusted to stop the ion beam at 30-50 mm in front
15 Si detectors with an active area of 10x10 mm2
and 350 um thickness at the back end of the chamber
to detect particles at different angles including
8 monitor detectors placed around the entrance
window at a distance of 80 mm from it to detect ions
of the beam elastically scattered from entrance foil
